	<div class="posts">
	<a name="94700654">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://www.extremeprogramming.org/">Extreme Programming: A Gentle Introduction.</a>.&nbsp; Ah, that's it -- just use the right search engine.  Now we are getting somewhere.  Loads of links.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#94700654">Wednesday, May 21, 2003</a></span></div>
<br>
  <!-- 2002-11-08 Change date format to yyyy-mm-dd and bookmark it 
                2002-11-09 Tune the color and make a purplized link out of it -->
	

	<div class="posts">
	<a name="94700599">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://www.xp2002.org/">Welcome to XP 2003</a>.&nbsp; Drat, in Genoa next week.  Bummer.<br>
