	<div class="posts">
	<a name="94618590">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://web.media.mit.edu/~joep/SpectrumWeb/SpectrumX.html">Electronic Music Interfaces</a>.&nbsp; Here's an amazing find by Norman Frisa on the interface between musicians and their instruments, with the prospects for new interfaces for electronic music just part of it. A very comprehensive overview by Joseph Paradiso at the MIT Media Lab.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#94618590">Monday, May 19, 2003</a></span></div>
<br>
